      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "- First you will need to place down your player units. To do so click
    any three empty tiles on the board. \n- To play an attack card click on your
    player unit and click and drag the card to the upper part of the board. Then
    click the enemy that you wish to attack with that card. To play a buff or heal
    click a player unit drag the card to the upper part of the screen then click
    the unit again.\n-Timelines this is a parallel world where you will have to jump
    to to protect. You can use the timelines to change the tide of battle."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
