  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '- Chaser: 26 HP moves 3 spaces a turn, and can attack your base or friendly
    units if they are cardinally adjacent to it for 6 damage.

    - Ranged unit:
    18 HP moves 2 spaces a turn and targets your player units. it can attack 5 tiles
    in all cardinal directions for 5 damage.

    -Healer: 20HP can move 2 spaces
    a turn and targets damaged enemy units if it gets cardinally adjacent to a damaged
    unit it will heal them 4 HP a turn.

    - Base Eater: 40 HP only targets the
    base moves 1 space a turn and it will do 10 damage every turn it is cardinally
    adjacent to you base.

    - Warper: 23 HP moves 2 spaces a turn and can target
    2 spaces in any cardinal direction. At the begining of the game it will create
    it''s own timeline and it will attack your friendly units and base in the timeline
    you are playing in for 5 damage. '
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
